      • checkText

        public void checkText​(java.lang.String text)
        Allows the System to check if the text written by the Specialist Doctor is right, according to the acceptance criteria. Checks if the text is blank or if it has more than four hundred words.
        Parameters:
        text - Text/Body to be checked.
